OL,3,CFormer police officer jailed for
OL,4,Ctaking covert pictures of crime victim
OL,6,FA former police officer has been
OL,7,Fjailed after he took two naked images
OL,8,Fof a vulnerable 16-year-old girl from
OL,9,Fher phone and covertly took pictures
OL,10,Fof another female victim's chest.
OL,12,FJoel Choudhury, a response constable
OL,13,Ffor Lancashire Police's South
OL,14,FDivision, first came to the attention
OL,15,Fof the force's Anti-Corruption Unit
OL,16,F(ACU) after an unrelated investigation
OL,17,Fhighlighted his "concerning behaviour".
OL,19,FHe was arrested in May 2023 and
OL,20,Fsuspended from duty pending his
OL,21,Fconduct.
