OL,3,CFormer police officer jailed for
OL,4,Ctaking covert pictures of crime victim
OL,6,FBut in the course of the investigation
OL,7,Fthe 44-year-old's mobile phone was
OL,8,Fexamined, where experts found the
OL,9,Fconcerning images he had captured
OL,10,Fwhile on duty.
OL,12,FOfficers found two naked images of a
OL,13,Fvulnerable 16-year-old girl he had
OL,14,Fcaptured off her phone, and five
OL,15,Fcovertly taken images of a vulnerable
OL,16,Ffemale victim of crime which showed
OL,17,Fher chest area, which had been taken
OL,18,Fin her living room.
