OL,3,CFormer police officer jailed for
OL,4,Ctaking covert pictures of crime victim
OL,6,FThey also uncovered two images of a
OL,7,Fmobile lock screen showing a selfie of
OL,8,Fa naked woman, which he had taken from
OL,9,Fthe mobile phone of the woman's former
OL,10,Fpartner after he had been arrested.
OL,12,FChoudhury, of no fixed address, was
OL,13,Fcharged with three counts of
OL,14,Fmisconduct in public office and making
OL,15,Findecent images of child, relating to
OL,16,Fthe photographs he had taken off the
OL,17,F16-year-old girl's mobile phone.
