OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F399A1733595738
OL,3,CFormer police officer jailed for
OL,4,Ctaking covert pictures of crime victim
OL,6,FHe pleaded guilty to the offences at
OL,7,FManchester Crown Court in June, and
OL,8,Fwas added to the Sex Offenders
OL,9,FRegister at that time.
OL,11,FHe has now been jailed for 16 months
OL,12,Fand given a seven year Sexual Harm
OL,13,FPrevention Order.
OL,15,FChoudhury resigned from the force
OL,16,Fwhile under investigation, but an
OL,17,Faccelerated misconduct hearing was
OL,18,Fheld in June where gross misconduct
OL,19,Fwas proved.
