OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F399A1733595738
OL,3,CFormer police officer jailed for
OL,4,Ctaking covert pictures of crime victim
OL,6,FHe was added to the Barred List, which
OL,7,Fprevents him from ever working in law
OL,8,Fenforcement.
OL,10,FDetective Chief Inspector Pete Reil,
OL,11,Ffrom our Anti-Corruption Unit (ACU),
OL,12,Fsaid: "Choudhury's behaviour was
OL,13,Fcompletely reprehensible and not
OL,14,Fcompatible with anyone who has the
OL,15,Fprivilege of wearing a police uniform.
OL,17,F"I welcome the sentence handed down
OL,18,Fand hope it demonstrates to the public
OL,19,Fthat this behaviour will not be
OL,20,Ftolerated by Lancashire Constabulary
OL,21,For the courts."
