OL,6,FHe added: "I want to make it clear
OL,7,Fthat the overwhelming majority of
OL,8,Fpolice officers in Lancashire are law
OL,9,Fabiding, respectful and go to work to
OL,10,Fmake a difference in the communities
OL,11,Fin which they serve.
OL,13,F"Where there is any evidence of
OL,14,Fwrongdoing by an officer or staff
OL,15,Fmember, our ACU will identify it,
OL,16,Finvestigate it and work with the Crown
OL,17,FProsecution Service to take the
OL,18,Fappropriate action."
